{"tid":2285234,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"依家嘅ARM Mac 就等同AMD Zen 1前夕咁","createTime":"2020-11-14T02:33:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-18T07:07:33.000Z","uid":124690,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"82f12c846991d11bca26e46a4aec9672995455f0","tid":2285234,"uid":124690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T02:33:55.000Z","msg":"個個都踩，個個都唔睇好。<br />\n結果Zen 1係點大家有目共睹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nARM on Mac 諗唔到有咩會失敗嘅可能。成個生態都係俾apple操控住，再且mac 最出名嘅final cut pro都係自己友。<br />\n<br />\n第一，成個os 都係Apple 揸莊，佢要改，要點整根本冇人阻止得到佢。依家吹啖啲人先係最on9嘅行為，人地講到明2-3年過渡，除非預部野用兩年，咁就你贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二，想當年都係由power架構轉過嚟x86。點解會覺得Arm( risc)係冇辦法玩到mac? 依家只係還原返之前嘅做法。<br />\n<br />\n第三，自己整cpu俾自己用可以俾對自己嘅產品提供一個最大化嘅tuning 。例子有ios 。<br />\n<br />\n第四，adobe都講左會同Apple合力開法，而早喺發佈apple silicon 嗰陣已經示範左用Apple A12Z去剪4K同photoshop 。所以我就真係唔明有乜好驚。<br />\n<br />\n咁虛擬化呢啲都的確係暫時未知嘅短板。但又真係有幾多會拎嚟用virtual windows? 同埋買得mac, 就正成正經用mac la<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a41b835ac13a6b7d4344a6bde7f54c3ea345dd45","tid":2285234,"uid":62452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T07:59:56.000Z","msg":"巴打，之前自動化workflow你覆我post但唔得求教🙇🏻&zwj;♂️"},{"pid":"105056b7fe495b2ff3f09c382a21841e68af247d","tid":2285234,"uid":62452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a41b835ac13a6b7d4344a6bde7f54c3ea345dd45","tid":2285234,"uid":62452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T07:59:56.000Z","msg":"巴打，之前自動化workflow你覆我post但唔得求教🙇🏻&zwj;♂️"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T08:03:22.000Z","msg":"同埋冇執行前先詢問要人手禁執行"},{"pid":"0a9e18cbd2549f64aaad3d58b789310ea4aa267e","tid":2285234,"uid":287326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T08:11:32.000Z","msg":"你以為vm淨係用來裝window？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3201496e678bc7a56a80c4d3f9d0